Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Located in the Altona Logistics Park, the West’s foremost industrial and logistics precinct, this opportunity represents a rare chance to secure one of the last positions in this tightly held location.

This fully functional transport depot and corporate office is ready for immediate occupation with capacity to extend the current facility or completely redevelop the property.

67-85 Toll Drive is highly connected to critical road, rail and shipping infrastructure. The property is only 2.5km from the Westgate Freeway, accessible via a full diamond interchange, 8km from the Port of Melbourne and 12km from the CBD.

The features of the site include:

- Site area of 20,080sqm*
- Modern 520sqm* office
- Concrete hardstand area of 8,473sqm*
- Additional undeveloped land area of 6,800sqm*
- Separate car park for 52 vehicles
- Fully fenced and landscaped facility with secure electric sliding gates
- Unencumbered truck movements on the extra wide 15m carriageway of Toll Drive
- Floodlights, a triple interceptor pit and wash bay facilities
- Easy access to Victoria’s vital road networks including Westgate Fwy, Western Ring Rd, Deer Park Bypass & CityLink

*approx.

- Land Area: 18,200sqm* (1.82ha*)
- 191m frontage to Toll Drive
- Corner Site
- 10km from Melbourne CBD and Ports*

*approx
